{"tid":1387623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[生命誠可貴] 各位一定要upgrade防彈頭盔","createTime":"2019-07-30T14:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T20:15:52.000Z","uid":57076,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"eae8296fab8c41c61eb6c9dd3f1f1b4af85cef72","tid":1387623,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:42:54.000Z","msg":"見到好多同學仔仲戴緊安全帽<br />\n仆街，打緊杖啊，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中彈有機會死人架</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XJv7kte.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXJv7kte.jpg&h=105b2ff4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你睇下粒海綿彈，鋼板都穿<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5MN19mH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5MN19mH.jpg&h=736e89bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以最低基本要求，係買PASGT防彈頭盔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JbZskua.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJbZskua.jpg&h=9661a900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.accstoreonline.com/products/pasgt-m88-helmet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.accstoreonline.com%2Fproducts%2Fpasgt-m88-helmet&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNhV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=961886ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.accstoreonline.com/products/pasgt-m88-helmet</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPASGT能抵擋重1.1克的硬物以每秒620公尺的速率射來，例如：<br />\n一發點四五口徑手槍彈從7公尺處射來，祇會在PASGT頭盔造成凹陷，無法穿透，因此PASGT可以抵擋戰場上的破片和斜向射來的子彈，但如果是被步槍彈正面命中的話仍可以打穿。5.56&times;45mm NATO子彈可在300公尺處貫穿PASGT盔。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">各位家長，有錢出錢有力出力，麻煩買多d高級頭盔比前線<br />\n<br />\n如果有更好提議都可以提出<br />\n<br />\n最後一句: 生命誠可貴，自由價更高<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"2e09254687c3a8b374fb1c57384b8168a0eb47a7","tid":1387623,"uid":293012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:44:08.000Z","msg":"組織全民玩快閃！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1387461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1387461</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n槍都用唔到咪仲好？"},{"pid":"1ff76670da4062eeae3c13060c56da9af01cb8fe","tid":1387623,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:48:36.000Z","msg":"呢個咁平真係樓主個講緊個款？定仿製wargame款黎？"},{"pid":"7012d6db64ca1c2334b8c05eefdcf38db9be2b9e","tid":1387623,"uid":268474,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:49:41.000Z","msg":"假野唔防彈架"},{"pid":"dcf27734ddb9eb4d031db5db3b6e5a77f2cbef55","tid":1387623,"uid":57076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1ff76670da4062eeae3c13060c56da9af01cb8fe","tid":1387623,"uid":129066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:48:36.000Z","msg":"呢個咁平真係樓主個講緊個款？定仿製wargame款黎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55d0147f432fb111462d715382f49bb2d5e2fe9","tid":1387623,"uid":66208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:59:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KjnEV9q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKjnEV9q.png&h=2210d791&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41ee7f77d090c83cd2459d2d86c4edd61b4c64fa","tid":1387623,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T20:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0530a8b88571af41a320d9cd3fb243c094d5cf5","tid":1387623,"uid":58616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T20:10:52.000Z","msg":"唔洗100都防到彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e9944e45d62e395dddfaf0651d8531e58007991","tid":1387623,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T20:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f51c87a29e27b38ba95